{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10109141746837-3":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10109141746837-3","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100124826694-4","P_10100124826694-5","P_10100124826694-6"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":96,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;\"><strong>爱国诗人陆游</strong><br></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">陆游是宋朝著名的爱国诗人，他从小就受到了父亲的教育，立下了报国之志。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">那年，他<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">参加礼部举行的考试，以优异的成绩获得了第一名，但遭到了大奸臣秦桧的打击，被除掉了姓名。然而，这一打击并没有使陆游灰心。回家以后，他仍然刻苦地攻读兵书，认真练武，准备建功立业。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">陆游三十多岁时当上了一个县官的属员。后来，担任了一个较大的官职。可没过多久，他又一次因为主张北伐，受到了投降派的排挤，被罢免回乡。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">十几年后，主战派将领王炎聘陆游至幕中襄理军务，使陆游的生活发生了很大的变化，他真正过上了军旅生活。在军旅生活中，他竭尽全力为收复祖国北方的失地而努力。他多次亲临前线视</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">察。由于他深深感受到广大人民渴望收复失地的强烈愿望，所以他在那几年写下了不少爱国诗篇。后来，因南宋皇帝屈膝投降，陆游的愿望又一次破灭了。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">陆游八十多岁时，仍念念不忘北伐，念念不忘收复北方的大好河山。有一天，他的身体已十分虚弱，躺在床上动也不能动，眼睛也失去了光彩，嘴里不停地喘着粗气。可是，当他看到了乡亲们和他的儿子来到他眼前时，他又振作起来，要儿子把纸和笔拿来。当他的儿子把纸和笔捧到他跟前时，他用力支撑着，写下了《示儿》这首诗：死去元知万事空，<span style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-decoration: underline;\">　　　　　　　</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-decoration: none;\">。王师北定中原日，</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-decoration: underline;\">　　　　　　　</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-decoration: none;\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">陆游虽然逝世了，但他的爱国诗篇却永远流传了下来，直到今天还激励着千万人的斗志。</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>请补充完整《示儿》这首诗。</p><p><span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">死去元知万事空，</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">__$$__</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"></span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">王师北定中原日，</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-decoration: none;\">__$$__。</span></p>","answers":[{"answer":"但悲不见九州同","subAnswers":["但悲不见九州同"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000690371","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"家祭无忘告乃翁","subAnswers":["家祭无忘告乃翁"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000690371","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":4,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"从文中可以看出，陆游能写下不少爱国诗篇的主要原因是（　）。","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutio